comment:
* Additional data mixed in with {@link StatusColumns} to link
     * back to specific {@link ContactsContract.Data#_ID} entries.
     *
     * @see StatusUpdates

variables.name: DATA_ID
variables.comment:
* Reference to the {@link Data#_ID} entry that owns this presence. *

Type: INTEGER

variables.name: PROTOCOL
variables.comment:
* See {@link CommonDataKinds.Im} for a list of defined protocol constants. *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: CUSTOM_PROTOCOL
variables.comment:
* Name of the custom protocol. Should be supplied along with the {@link #PROTOCOL} value * {@link ContactsContract.CommonDataKinds.Im#PROTOCOL_CUSTOM}. Should be null or * omitted if {@link #PROTOCOL} value is not * {@link ContactsContract.CommonDataKinds.Im#PROTOCOL_CUSTOM}. * *

Type: NUMBER

variables.name: IM_HANDLE
variables.comment:
* The IM handle the presence item is for. The handle is scoped to * {@link #PROTOCOL}. *

Type: TEXT

variables.name: IM_ACCOUNT
variables.comment:
* The IM account for the local user that the presence data came from. *

Type: TEXT
